{"tid":319254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻鳩傳心師喺高登開po𨳒㭍cable放蛇","createTime":"2017-07-12T15:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T16:57:14.000Z","uid":117993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"504b31f0747bb216e637996b6d8d58d101c2d5e8","tid":319254,"uid":117993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6751134&amp;type=CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6751134%26type%3DCA&d=GKMjGILKcLxoFPmyzF3RFP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f50785b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6751134&amp;type=CA</a>"},{"pid":"6a41ec77dc0937e76b471463303ef9ac41e00125","tid":319254,"uid":117993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"//情況就好似你放針，拎篇英文比5個垃圾翻譯人做translate，5個人都譯到9唔答8，再去工聯會報個課程Hi9佢廢，然後一棍打死成船人<br />\n<br />\n當然新聞唔會咁做，因為大家default認為世界上係有班勁既翻譯，呢班人係有料的<br />\n<br />\n好似傳心師呢D大家都唔熟，又要講及D 心物二元論既課題，對本身宗教意識薄弱既香港人來講，default就已經唔信，再加一篇擺明係有陷阱位既報導，仲唔全城起哄發洩<br />\n<br />\n陷阱唔係指隻膠龜，係講個記者未必只係訪問5個人，可能佢訪10個，其中5件垃圾講隻膠龜點點點，同埋記者只係去左最廢既工聯會course做針，佢有去過知名度高甚至有國際級數既傳心機構做專訪咩？無<br />\n<br />\n香港本來就多騙子，個邏輯本身唔應該係「所有傳心師都係騙子」，而係「有騙子去左做傳心師」，做新聞既人叫人提防好合理，但用呢種偏頗既方法去報，就好似因為倫敦金既存在而去否認成個黃金市場既運作<br />\n<br />\n再講返傳唔傳心呢樣野，本身就好似中醫望聞問切，同埋最早人地只係做貓同狗，因為呢兩種生物入屋歷史已經有幾萬年，演化左一套body language同facial expression，傳心師本來就係一門下苦功學五﹑六年先可以出道既行業，而家比班蛋散搞到神神化化，比人踢爆係佢地抵死，但因為行業有神棍而比社會杯葛呢個行業，個方向似乎已經//"},{"pid":"c9a918443436eacf127425b48ef7097565db0cf1","tid":319254,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6751134&amp;type=CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6751134%26type%3DCA&d=GKMjGILKcLxoFPmyzF3RFP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f50785b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6751134&amp;type=CA</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"96118759791aeff84c923131c64c8abd6f8f3212","tid":319254,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fedb0883b2641d49c60e5d094007c7e5c087e58","tid":319254,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"同樣系狂信徒思維護教<br />\n好想知熱血時報點睇動物傳心呢單野🤔"},{"pid":"ec59e72961b26146b719a3353fc760fe9059505a","tid":319254,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"咁都可以扯埋落去心物二元論度講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笛卡兒都俾你激到返生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42952ef2866e8df53cbf7a3f369912538251e438","tid":319254,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"睇得出條友已經比傳心術邪教洗撚左個豬腦, 冇撚得救"},{"pid":"3b3c40d745329e5ab6014c6bcaf25245d434794a","tid":319254,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"，係講個記者未必只係訪問5個人，可能佢訪10個，其中5件垃圾講隻膠龜點點點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲明咪講咗搵得5個"},{"pid":"b6219c375ad8f9db79c0774bab8f0be661c34fca","tid":319254,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}